Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們，先生們，晚上好。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:46.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,La mort n'est jamais qu'un salut,ainsi mon ami a t'il murmurer jadis amon intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死不過是解脫」我的朋友曾這樣對我說。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:51.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,asupposer que la mort soit un salut,que veux tu donner quand atoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「若死是解脫，那你究竟想帶給他們什麼呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:52.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,mon ami arépondu en un souffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只回答了一句話。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:58.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,Chez eux une souffrance et un remord éternel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我要給他們永遠的痛苦與悔恨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我不會再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二幕\N反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的選擇真的是正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就沒什麼真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂真理是在自己的信念之下創造出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使同室操戈 甚至拋棄父母也在所不惜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能光看父母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要看眼前的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在弗朗茲死去的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我聽了您的告白後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就一直走到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著波光粼漓的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚就止不住地湧了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我還清楚地記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲給我留下了幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對不要恨任何人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愛人的心情和恨人的心情」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最初都是由思念之情中產生的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為愛德蒙最後的單身之夜乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙·唐泰斯在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受莫爾塞夫將軍之命前來迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍即將進入巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將建立臨時政府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之內莫爾塞夫大統領即將誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我去 到他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…費爾南·蒙代戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民議會被我們東方宇宙軍佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是重大的叛逆行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承認 決不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…真無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您慎重發言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣國賊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在解散原議會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈巴黎進入戒嚴狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是個名叫愛德蒙·唐泰斯的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 直到那天我還對人毫無戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心祈禱著父親與未婚妻的幸福 渡過每日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現將你作為暗殺王子案的重大嫌疑人逮捕歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙 愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被告發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據那封告發信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你持有記載暗殺王子案真相的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長去世前 應該交託給你一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照船長的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備把信送到收件人那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巴黎 雞鷺街13號」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「諾瓦蒂埃先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信中寫有與暗殺王子案有關的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包括維爾福的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的我將信交給了當事人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你只是出色地完成了任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯先生 關於此信的事就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就會被釋放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 維爾福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知該如何感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻一定正焦急地等著我回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信的事你和別人說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 根據船長的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直堅守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道這封信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到現在還相信王子是被敵人暗殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是地球方面的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰爭中牟取暴利的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望戰爭繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗殺為最壞結局收場 和平無望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中他們下懷 紛爭擴大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗殺的報復為名 戰爭愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然…然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不幸的男人…被埋葬於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了我的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在經濟司法等界各自嶄露頭角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在軍事界爬到頂峰的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終向大統領的地位進發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫維爾福先生來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底犯了什麼罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在被收監入伊夫堡的我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無盡的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對付邊境外未知敵人的自動化要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也成了那控制系統的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 甚至連死亡的選擇也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無限的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不期望救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這身體消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些奪去我一切 把我逼向毀滅的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都受到最殘酷 最悲慘的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要給他們生不如死 永無止境的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le chagrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désir ardent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la résignation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la colère...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la terreur...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désespoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再一次希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et anouveau l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等待著像你這樣的人的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}cela fait des milliers d'années que j'attendais
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了借用這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}al'intérieur de ce coprs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數千年間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la venue de quelqu'un
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}comme...toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:03.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je suis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將與你同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Et tu es
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也與我同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec moi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借給你我的智慧和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je te donne ma sagesse et mon pouvoir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et toi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要獻出你的身體與心靈…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}tu m'offres ton esprit et ton corps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 我是命運的齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不過是這堅定的復仇之心在驅動著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我還是不希望您去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您打消這個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠命令基督山伯爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有基督山伯爵一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心中 難道已經…沒有任何人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經…已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙軍正向大學等機關移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請市民們盡快避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙軍正向大學等機關移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請市民們盡快避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的金子 我的金子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑 死刑 死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 別阻攔我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別關機喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對伯爵要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器儲藏庫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識一下我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱旋門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 巴黎終於被我征服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不應該是你所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我說的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿溢著更多希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 這是國民所必需的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是大統領夫人了 梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無所畏懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙就活在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是我未婚夫的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基督山伯爵的身份回到了我們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了復仇而回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇？你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和愛德蒙不是好友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼愛德蒙一定要向你復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他…是好友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不認為那傢伙是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你的漂亮話有多傷人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出讓他被捕的信的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將會是鋼鐵之艦法老號的船長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是個馬塞港的苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你的漂亮話讓愛德蒙墜入不幸的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我對你說了多麼過分的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開巴黎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭煩那種喪家犬般的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠只能望其項背的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留在 我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記和你度過的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 費爾南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深愛著她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我愛你…勝過一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那傢伙還活著 我也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你對我做的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要奪走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將繼續祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為父親 為母親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有為最重要的您之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三幕\N愛德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待
